---

---

<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}favicon.svg`} />
		<link rel="icon" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}favicon.ico`} />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Youdian</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="site-shell">
			<section class="hero">
				<p class="eyebrow">Youdian Demo</p>
				<h1>有点内容，从一篇文章开始</h1>
				<p class="intro">
					这是一个用于展示文章页面的轻量 demo。点击下方链接，可以查看
					Astro Markdown 页面在站点中的呈现方式。
				</p>
				<a class="article-card" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}articles/demo/`}>
					<span class="article-card__label">示例文章</span>
					<strong>有点：一篇 Demo 文章</strong>
					<span>阅读文章 →</span>
				</a>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		color: #172033;
		background: #f7f2ea;
		font-family:
			Inter, "Noto Sans SC", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", system-ui,
			sans-serif;
	}

	body {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 207, 128, 0.45), transparent 34rem),
			linear-gradient(135deg, #fffaf0 0%, #eef4ff 100%);
	}

	.site-shell {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		display: grid;
		min-height: 100vh;
		place-items: center;
		padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
	}

	.hero {
		max-width: 46rem;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: #b45309;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.16em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
		line-height: 1.05;
	}

	.intro {
		margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
		max-width: 38rem;
		color: #465367;
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.article-card {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		max-width: 27rem;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.12);
		border-radius: 1.25rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
		box-shadow: 0 1rem 3rem rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.08);
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition:
			transform 160ms ease,
			box-shadow 160ms ease;
	}

	.article-card:hover,
	.article-card:focus-visible {
		transform: translateY(-0.15rem);
		box-shadow: 0 1.25rem 3rem rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.14);
	}

	.article-card__label {
		color: #6b7280;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.article-card strong {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}
</style>
